com.microsoft.azure.management.network

Interface NetworkInterface.DefinitionWithPublicIpAddress

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Creatable<NetworkInterface>, Indexable, NetworkInterface.DefinitionCreatable, NetworkInterface.DefinitionWithNetworkSecurityGroup, Resource.DefinitionWithTags<NetworkInterface.DefinitionCreatable>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    NetworkInterface.Definitions
    Enclosing interface:
    NetworkInterface

    public static interface NetworkInterface.DefinitionWithPublicIpAddress
extends NetworkInterface.DefinitionCreatable
    The stage of the network interface definition allowing to associate public IP address with it's primary Ip configuration.
